## üìä Experimental Results

We conducted extensive testing on the BIS dataset. The **Small (s)** variant of YOLOv8 proved to be the optimal choice, outperforming both the Nano and Medium variants in mAP50.

### 1. Quantitative Performance
| Model Variant | Parameters | mAP50 | Inference Speed |
| :--- | :---: | :---: | :---: |
| üöÄ YOLOv8n-Seg (Nano) | ~3.2M | 0.628 | Fastest |
| ‚öñÔ∏è **YOLOv8s-Seg (Small)** | **~11.2M** | **0.651** | **Balanced** |
| üß† YOLOv8m-Seg (Medium) | ~25.9M | 0.613 | Slower |

